author: Jamela Alindogan
title: Philippines Easter celebrations: Catholics mark holy week
description: More than 200 Filipinos have died from the virus and the number is expected to rise.
content:
Catholics in the Philippines have marked the holy week behind closed doors after President Rodrigo Duterte ordered a lockdown to curb the spread of the novel coronavirus.
